After the treatment, the blood and main organs were harvested and applied for the biosafety evaluation T-GCDs. According to the results of blood biochemical, blood routine examinations, and H&E staining of the main organs (
                              Fig. S6
                           ), there were no significant pathological changes among the control, periodontitis and T-GCDs groups. It strongly demonstrated that T-GCDs were safe for applications in vivo.
